cdata.name: Arcade City
cdata.desc: Arcade City is a peer-to-peer ride sharing network based on the Ethereum blockchain. It is a self governing network, meaning it is owned and operated by the drivers. ARC is an ERC20 token that serves as a currency on Arcade City's ecosytem. It is also offer as a reward to users that take actions in order to grow the network, i.e. providing a well-reviewed service, recruiting new drivers, etc.
